highlights.text: “Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 909 days straight.
Grupo Menos É Mais has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “P do Pecado - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #1.
“Saudade e Cabelos Brancos” by Gusttavo Lima is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 84 spots at #112.
“Um Maluco Cowboy - Ao Vivo” by CountryBeat is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #173.
